        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3575512384" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10179511479221790">This was a page-turner and made me want to keep reading right from the very beginning! The story was realistic, but there are also elements of surprising magic, making for a nice blend of two genres: realistic fiction and fantasy. An emotional story that made me think about family, love, and connection, this is a must read!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


